<<File System Value storage>>

  Holds Values in flat FileSystem files. <<path>> property points to root directory to store files

------------
   <value-storage class="org.exoplatform.services.jcr.impl.storage.value.fs.SimpleFileValueStorage">
       <properties>
          <property name="path" value="target/temp/values"/>
       </properties>
--------------

  Where :

  path - a location where value files will be stored
